  "description": "Grab a bite from the snack bar/deli serving guests of Residence Inn By Marriott Long Island Hauppauge. Mingle with other guests at the complimentary reception, held on select days. A complimentary hot/cold buffet breakfast is served daily.\n\nBe sure to enjoy recreational amenities, including an indoor pool, a spa tub, and a 24-hour fitness center. Additional features at this aparthotel include complimentary wireless Internet access, a fireplace in the lobby, and a picnic area.\n\nFeatured amenities include a 24-hour business center, express check-out, and complimentary newspapers in the lobby. Planning an event in Hauppauge? This hotel has 750 square feet (68 square meters) of space consisting of conference space and a meeting room. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite.\n\nDistances are displayed to the nearest 0.1 mile and kilometer. \n Nissequogue River - 1.2 km / 0.7 mi \n Stonebridge Golf Links and Country Club - 1.8 km / 1.1 mi \n Blydenburgh County Park - 1.8 km / 1.1 mi \n Hauppauge Industrial Park - 3.1 km / 1.9 mi \n Connetquot River - 4.9 km / 3 mi \n Lakeland County Park - 4.9 km / 3.1 mi \n Connetquot River State Park - 4.2 km / 2.6 mi \n Caleb Smith State Park - 6.3 km / 3.9 mi \n SUSA Orlin & Cohen Sports Complex - 7.1 km / 4.4 mi \n Bethpage Ballpark - 7.3 km / 4.5 mi \n Suffolk County Community College - Michael J. Grant Campus West - 7.6 km / 4.7 mi \n Lake Ronkonkoma - 7.8 km / 4.9 mi \n Cohalan Court Complex - 7.8 km / 4.9 mi \n St. Catherine Of Siena Medical Center - 8.1 km / 5 mi \n Alfonse M. D Amato United States Courthouse - 8.2 km / 5.1 mi \n \nThe nearest airports are:\nMacArthur Airport (ISP) - 11.6 km / 7.2 mi\n Farmingdale, NY (FRG-Republic) - 31 km / 19.3 mi\n Shirley, NY (WSH-Brookhaven Calabro) - 30.3 km / 18.9 mi\n Bridgeport, CT (BDR-Igor I. Sikorsky Memorial) - 141.6 km / 88 mi\n Westhampton, NY (FOK-Francis S. Gabreski) - 53.2 km / 33 mi\n \nThe preferred airport for Residence Inn By Marriott Long Island Hauppauge is MacArthur Airport (ISP).",
